The paper focuses on deep metric learning (DML) for image retrieval, verification, and classification, which falls under computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also discusses the use of various machine learning techniques and algorithms for DML, which falls under machine learning (cs.LG). Additionally, the paper evaluates the performance of these algorithms on different datasets, which falls under multimedia (cs.MM) and information retrieval (cs.IR). Finally, the paper discusses the state-of-the-art performance achieved by the evaluated algorithms, which falls under artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
